this is a great opportunity which cannot be wasted we understand 
the significance of obligations resulting from the warsaw pact to 
all its members i state that the government that i will form will 
respect this treaty 
high chamber 
the change in polands political situation stems from the fact 
that the new government is formed on solidaritys initiative in 
agreement with united peasants party and democratic party 
this is perceived as an extraordinary event in our political life 
the possibility that every force in parliament could form the 
government must become something completely normal 
the government i am forming does not assume responsibility for 
the legacy it inherits however that influences the circumstances in 
which we must function 
we separate ourselves from the past with a thick line we will be 
