i am aware that for my compatriots today the most important 
question is whether it could be better 
we will all reply to this the success of the activities of the 
future government depends on whether it will be accepted and 
understood by the society 
all social and political forces represented in the parliament and 
those existing outside must define their position in the face of the 
new situation 
it poses a challenge for everyone and especially for the young 
generation which must take notice of a great opportunity to solve 
the challenges we face 
the government will not cure anything we must do it together 
poland will be different if everybody wants it 
