harvey korman and cloris leachman as the respectively officious 
and bizarre staff of a large unlikely new york hotel 
spencers first show an homage to his hero mel brooks and 
brooks 1960s satirical spy comedy get smart was abcs sledge 
hammer like get smart it was heavy on inside jokes and 
physical gags 
this time around spencer is not gazing from afar but is paired 
with his idol producerdirector brooks cowrote the pilot with 
