electronics businesses of rca corp and general electric co on 
wednesday was named president and chief operating officer of lowell 
massbased wang 
wang portrayed him as a turnaround specialist who could help the 
minicomputer company recover from last years 424 million loss and 
the defection of some nervous customers 
miller never has worked for a computer company but an wang the 
companys 69yearold founder and chairman praised him in a 
