resolving the companys current situation and restoring it to 
profitability 
miller replaces frederick wang the son and former heir apparent 
of the founder who resigned aug 8 as the companys financial 
troubles mounted harry hs chou served as president in the interim 
wang stock rose 25 cents to close at 625 a share wednesday on 
the american stock exchange 
