allowed suits against other defendants the companies have said 
suits against the other potential defendants would result in claims 
for indemnity against the trust defending those claims would 
distract the trustees and reduce the amount of money available to 
pay claims the companies contend 
about 118000 claims still are pending and would be resolved 
