basic agreement on economic issues throughout the 
philadelphiabased bell atlantic system was reached a week ago 
talks on local issues with bell of pennsylvania and diamond state 
telephone in delaware are still snagged the cwa said 
elsewhere among the bell operating companies cwa representatives 
